%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

       coderemarks - LaTeX package for annotating source code.

             Copyright (C) 2010 Miek Gieben

%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

Using this package you can annotate your source code with extra
explanation(s). In the source code a circle with a number is drawn.
After the code you display the numbers and the text of the remarks.
Two commands are provided:
\longremark{...} use this to create your remarks.
\showremark      use this *after* the code to display all remarks

